  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/46702fcb37d81e1327bddc4ceed656df.avif?t=1723878860\" width=600 height=196 /></span><br><br><strong><u><u>Backstory</u></u></strong><br><br>Random, Sarah and Luciana are three teenagers who do not know each other yet. They also do not know that they hold a very special power inside of them.<br>But someone knows. An evil god. His goal is to lure the three of them into the deadliest of traps and absorb their power. Will he succeed? Or can you lead the soon-to-become heroes to face and defeat their worst nightmare? Play this oustanding adventure and find out!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/59f8e828678eda7151f7196134b2b070.poster.avif?t=1723878860\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/59f8e828678eda7151f7196134b2b070.webm?t=1723878860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/59f8e828678eda7151f7196134b2b070.mp4?t=1723878860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Details</u></strong><br><br>3 Stars of Destiny is a fantastic 2D RPG by the makers of the Millennium series and The Book of Legends. In this extensive adventure, explore countless unique places, defeat tons of enemies and complete richly developed quests. The game features addictive gameplay and an adventure worth tens of hours of playtime.<br><br>3 Stars of Destiny was rated: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>4.2/5</strong> by <i>Gamersgate</i> players<br></li><li><strong>4.9/5</strong> by <i>Big Fish Games</i> players</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/752cb06694aae3acd7438b5a2ac9f8f1.poster.avif?t=1723878860\" width=600 height=42 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/752cb06694aae3acd7438b5a2ac9f8f1.webm?t=1723878860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/752cb06694aae3acd7438b5a2ac9f8f1.mp4?t=1723878860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Key Features:</u></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 achievements to unlock<br></li><li>80 hours of playing<br></li><li>10 Legendary Heroes<br></li><li>50 Quests<br></li><li>9 Relics and Artifacts to discover</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/46702fcb37d81e1327bddc4ceed656df.avif?t=1723878860\" width=600 height=196 /></span><br><br><strong><u><u>Backstory</u></u></strong><br><br>Random, Sarah and Luciana are three teenagers who do not know each other yet. They also do not know that they hold a very special power inside of them.<br>But someone knows. An evil god. His goal is to lure the three of them into the deadliest of traps and absorb their power. Will he succeed? Or can you lead the soon-to-become heroes to face and defeat their worst nightmare? Play this oustanding adventure and find out!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/59f8e828678eda7151f7196134b2b070.poster.avif?t=1723878860\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/59f8e828678eda7151f7196134b2b070.webm?t=1723878860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/278530/extras/59f8e828678eda7151f7196134b2b070.mp4?t=1723878860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Details</u></strong><br><br>3 Stars of Destiny is a fantastic 2D RPG by the makers of the Millennium series and The Book of Legends. In this extensive adventure, explore countless unique places, defeat tons of enemies and complete richly developed quests. The game features addictive gameplay and an adventure worth tens of hours of playtime.<br><br>3 Stars of Destiny was rated: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>4.2/5</strong> by <i>Gamersgate</i> players<br></li><li><strong>4.9/5</strong> by <i>Big Fish Games</i> players</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\